1
00:00:13,480 --> 00:00:15,750
Defying the law
by unlawfully imprisoning others,

2
00:00:16,160 --> 00:00:18,320
attempting to murder
the heir of a marquis.

3
00:00:18,830 --> 00:00:20,070
What punishment should you face?

4
00:00:20,710 --> 00:00:21,640
Your Highness,

5
00:00:22,000 --> 00:00:23,710
though your status is noble,

6
00:00:24,120 --> 00:00:26,600
by ancestral law,
the women of the inner palace

7
00:00:26,610 --> 00:00:28,000
may not interfere in state affairs.

8
00:00:28,640 --> 00:00:29,830
This is a court of law,

9
00:00:29,850 --> 00:00:31,870
not a place for Your Highness
to make a spectacle.

10
00:00:32,110 --> 00:00:33,600
Please conduct yourself with dignity

11
00:00:33,600 --> 00:00:34,640
and leave at once.

12
00:00:34,710 --> 00:00:35,840
In that case,

13
00:00:35,960 --> 00:00:37,280
I'll remain here

14
00:00:37,280 --> 00:00:38,470
and go nowhere today.

15
00:00:39,150 --> 00:00:41,290
Everyone in and around this yamen
is under my command.

16
00:00:41,600 --> 00:00:42,880
Until the court sends someone

17
00:00:42,880 --> 00:00:45,030
to uncover the truth of this case,

18
00:00:45,240 --> 00:00:46,600
no one here,

19
00:00:46,600 --> 00:00:48,070
including you, Prefect Yu,

20
00:00:48,560 --> 00:00:50,200
may leave this yamen.

21
00:00:52,600 --> 00:00:53,880
Commandery Princess Zhaoning,

22
00:00:53,888 --> 00:00:56,250
how dare you place an imperial official
under house arrest!

23
00:00:56,350 --> 00:00:57,110
This matter,

24
00:00:57,390 --> 00:00:59,280
I will report to His Majesty at once.

25
00:00:59,920 --> 00:01:00,600
Mo Yuan.

26
00:01:04,230 --> 00:01:06,040
How dare you!

27
00:01:06,870 --> 00:01:08,510
I am an imperial official!

28
00:01:11,000 --> 00:01:11,920
Xihe!

29
00:01:12,640 --> 00:01:13,560
Xihe!

30
00:01:15,280 --> 00:01:16,200
Xihe!

31
00:01:18,560 --> 00:01:19,430
Xihe!

32
00:01:20,870 --> 00:01:21,790
Are you all right?

33
00:01:22,000 --> 00:01:22,680
I'm fine.

34
00:01:23,950 --> 00:01:24,920
Magistrate Tang

35
00:01:24,920 --> 00:01:26,920
has confessed everything.

36
00:01:27,150 --> 00:01:28,510
The secret prison in Zenan

37
00:01:28,510 --> 00:01:30,150
was orchestrated by Yu Zao.

38
00:01:31,870 --> 00:01:33,150
I am willing to testify.

39
00:01:33,510 --> 00:01:34,840
It was Yu Zao who ordered

40
00:01:35,120 --> 00:01:36,680
the people to be secretly abducted,

41
00:01:36,680 --> 00:01:38,150
forced to mine ore,

42
00:01:38,150 --> 00:01:39,430
and illegally forge weapons

43
00:01:39,430 --> 00:01:40,400
for a treasonous plot.

44
00:01:40,840 --> 00:01:42,480
I have kept the account books

45
00:01:42,590 --> 00:01:44,120
and correspondence as evidence.

46
00:01:44,210 --> 00:01:46,350
Tang Juan, you wretch!
May you die a miserable death!

47
00:01:46,350 --> 00:01:47,680
Throw Yu Zao into prison

48
00:01:47,680 --> 00:01:49,024
and keep him under strict guard.

49
00:02:03,480 --> 00:02:03,950
Kneel!

50
00:02:03,960 --> 00:02:05,030
The prefectural office
is handling this case.

51
00:02:05,040 --> 00:02:06,720
Drop your weapons
and you will be spared!

52
00:02:07,200 --> 00:02:07,870
Run!

53
00:02:08,590 --> 00:02:09,430
Cui Jinbai!

54
00:02:10,310 --> 00:02:11,310
Cui Jinbai!

55
00:02:12,080 --> 00:02:13,280
Cui Jinbai, where are you?

56
00:02:13,280 --> 00:02:13,776
Don't move!

57
00:02:16,030 --> 00:02:17,030
Come out!

58
00:02:18,080 --> 00:02:18,710
Hurry!

59
00:02:19,360 --> 00:02:20,310
Cui Jinbai!

60
00:02:26,030 --> 00:02:27,560
Stone Cui!

61
00:03:46,900 --> 00:03:47,712
=Blossoms of Power=

62
00:03:47,712 --> 00:03:50,500
(Adapted from the novel, After My
Bloom, All Flowers Wither by Jin Huang)

63
00:03:50,580 --> 00:03:53,540
=Episode 15=

64
00:03:56,030 --> 00:03:56,840
Hurry!

65
00:03:57,710 --> 00:03:58,560
Cui Jinbai!

66
00:03:58,620 --> 00:03:59,300
Hurry!

67
00:04:04,190 --> 00:04:05,310
Stone Cui!

68
00:04:06,710 --> 00:04:07,430
I'm here.

69
00:04:13,840 --> 00:04:14,560
How are you?

70
00:04:15,120 --> 00:04:15,870
Are you hurt?

71
00:04:15,870 --> 00:04:17,160
Did they... did they hurt you?

72
00:04:25,664 --> 00:04:27,160
Seeing how worried you are about me

73
00:04:28,720 --> 00:04:29,520
makes me very happy.

74
00:04:34,310 --> 00:04:35,040
Cui Jinbai,

75
00:04:38,000 --> 00:04:39,190
Yu Zao has been imprisoned,

76
00:04:39,200 --> 00:04:41,040
and the Prefectural Residence
has been seized.

77
00:04:41,480 --> 00:04:42,360
I'm grateful

78
00:04:42,680 --> 00:04:43,560
that you helped me.

79
00:04:44,240 --> 00:04:46,070
But what you said to me before,

80
00:04:46,070 --> 00:04:47,120
I hope you'll forget it.

81
00:04:47,480 --> 00:04:48,390
Do you understand?

82
00:04:48,400 --> 00:04:49,830
But you were clearly worried about me.

83
00:04:49,830 --> 00:04:51,024
That's because you helped me.

84
00:04:55,360 --> 00:04:55,870
Let's go.

85
00:05:17,920 --> 00:05:19,070
Greetings, Your Highness.

86
00:05:21,430 --> 00:05:22,480
These past few days,

87
00:05:25,120 --> 00:05:26,360
you have worked tirelessly.

88
00:05:26,720 --> 00:05:28,128
You flatter me, Your Highness.

89
00:05:30,520 --> 00:05:32,600
I'm not trying to interfere
with your investigation.

90
00:05:33,310 --> 00:05:34,950
I simply wish to remain by your side

91
00:05:35,360 --> 00:05:36,830
and be of some help to you.

92
00:05:36,928 --> 00:05:38,510
There's no need to trouble yourself.

93
00:05:38,900 --> 00:05:40,480
You should return to the palace at once,

94
00:05:40,704 --> 00:05:42,400
lest His Majesty become concerned.

95
00:05:46,920 --> 00:05:48,510
Though our wedding has been postponed,

96
00:05:49,070 --> 00:05:50,120
our goal remains the same.

97
00:05:50,500 --> 00:05:51,920
We both seek to eliminate corruption

98
00:05:51,920 --> 00:05:53,184
and bring justice to the people.

99
00:05:58,000 --> 00:05:59,040
I believe you

100
00:06:01,560 --> 00:06:04,070
also wish to solve Bu Shulin's
case as soon as possible.

101
00:06:04,720 --> 00:06:05,360
After all,

102
00:06:08,430 --> 00:06:09,680
you are as close as sisters.

103
00:06:24,950 --> 00:06:26,120
Throughout the interrogation,

104
00:06:27,120 --> 00:06:28,120
you will preside.

105
00:06:28,560 --> 00:06:29,560
I'll merely observe

106
00:06:30,430 --> 00:06:31,720
and lend my support.

107
00:06:33,904 --> 00:06:35,070
As you wish, Your Highness.

108
00:06:52,040 --> 00:06:53,000
Your Highness,

109
00:06:53,600 --> 00:06:56,000
there's no need
to waste your time on me.

110
00:06:56,560 --> 00:06:58,830
Hasn't Tang Juan already confessed?

111
00:06:59,120 --> 00:07:00,560
Whatever the sentence is,

112
00:07:00,920 --> 00:07:02,040
so be it.

113
00:07:02,430 --> 00:07:03,040
Yu Zao,

114
00:07:03,870 --> 00:07:05,070
you secretly transferred

115
00:07:05,270 --> 00:07:07,630
the imprisoned civilians
into the mountains to mine ore

116
00:07:07,720 --> 00:07:08,720
and forge weapons.

117
00:07:08,950 --> 00:07:10,040
But as far as I know,

118
00:07:10,270 --> 00:07:11,750
you hold no influence in the military.

119
00:07:11,760 --> 00:07:13,424
So the mastermind
behind the secret prison

120
00:07:13,430 --> 00:07:14,160
is not you.

121
00:07:14,560 --> 00:07:15,750
Who is the real mastermind?

122
00:07:18,000 --> 00:07:19,240
It's me.

123
00:07:20,928 --> 00:07:23,070
The secret prison
has caused countless tragedies.

124
00:07:23,270 --> 00:07:24,720
Families have been torn apart,

125
00:07:25,190 --> 00:07:26,270
and lives destroyed.

126
00:07:26,288 --> 00:07:27,610
Even if His Majesty
sentences your entire clan

127
00:07:27,616 --> 00:07:29,050
to death, it would not be excessive.

128
00:07:30,000 --> 00:07:30,750
Then...

129
00:07:32,310 --> 00:07:33,630
let it be.

130
00:07:34,950 --> 00:07:35,630
Yu Zao,

131
00:07:36,144 --> 00:07:38,190
have you not thought
of your wife and children?

132
00:07:38,190 --> 00:07:39,830
Or your brothers and sisters?

133
00:07:39,850 --> 00:07:41,408
Will you really stand by and watch them

134
00:07:41,440 --> 00:07:43,630
be dragged to their deaths
because of you?

135
00:07:59,390 --> 00:08:00,480
Yu Zao's attitude

136
00:08:00,830 --> 00:08:01,680
is very unusual.

137
00:08:02,160 --> 00:08:02,750
Indeed.

138
00:08:04,720 --> 00:08:05,750
He's far too confident.

139
00:08:08,160 --> 00:08:08,800
Your Highness,

140
00:08:09,920 --> 00:08:11,630
do you still remember
the Moon Palace game?

141
00:08:21,630 --> 00:08:22,550
Black can become white,

142
00:08:22,624 --> 00:08:23,830
and white can become black.

143
00:08:24,032 --> 00:08:25,970
In this world, it's more
than just a chess piece

144
00:08:25,984 --> 00:08:27,780
that blurs the line
between black and white.

145
00:08:45,600 --> 00:08:46,840
Truth can become false,

146
00:08:48,576 --> 00:08:49,790
and false can become truth.

147
00:08:51,088 --> 00:08:53,552
Yu Zao faces the punishment
of extermination of the whole clan.

148
00:08:53,632 --> 00:08:55,550
Yet in prison,
he has remained remarkably calm,

149
00:08:55,840 --> 00:08:58,320
without offering a single word
in defense of his wife or clan.

150
00:08:58,750 --> 00:09:00,416
That means
there's a strong possibility...

151
00:09:00,432 --> 00:09:01,360
The Yu Zao in prison

152
00:09:01,870 --> 00:09:03,120
is not the real Yu Zao.

153
00:09:03,910 --> 00:09:04,910
Whether he's real or not,

154
00:09:05,360 --> 00:09:07,200
that depends on your next.

155
00:09:24,784 --> 00:09:26,256
I've kept you waiting, Your Highness.

156
00:09:27,120 --> 00:09:27,630
Not for long.

157
00:09:28,096 --> 00:09:29,472
When it comes to waiting for you,

158
00:09:29,632 --> 00:09:30,960
I have all the time in the world.

159
00:09:33,790 --> 00:09:36,080
Why is it that you can always
say such flirtatious things

160
00:09:36,480 --> 00:09:37,840
as if they were nothing?

161
00:09:37,904 --> 00:09:39,550
Because every word comes from the heart.

162
00:09:39,600 --> 00:09:41,296
If this is how
the conversation is going,

163
00:09:41,440 --> 00:09:42,440
I'll be leaving now.

164
00:09:42,960 --> 00:09:43,670
All right.

165
00:09:44,320 --> 00:09:45,720
Let's talk about something else.

166
00:09:53,600 --> 00:09:54,600
These documents

167
00:09:55,240 --> 00:09:57,030
are evidence
that Yu Zao accepted bribes.

168
00:09:57,030 --> 00:09:58,630
Every payment can be traced.

169
00:09:58,944 --> 00:10:01,150
Yet not a single payment
went to his wife or children.

170
00:10:01,720 --> 00:10:03,670
(Private Records of the Ningze Prefectural Treasury)
Nor did any of it go to his relatives.

171
00:10:04,390 --> 00:10:06,200
All the money ended up in one place.

172
00:10:06,790 --> 00:10:07,390
Yuzhou.

173
00:10:19,550 --> 00:10:21,080
You dropped this the other day.

174
00:10:30,750 --> 00:10:31,960
I'll be there on time tomorrow.

175
00:10:42,000 --> 00:10:42,840
Prefect Yu,

176
00:10:42,896 --> 00:10:45,312
your crimes warrant
the extermination of your whole clan,

177
00:10:45,440 --> 00:10:46,870
yet you don't even flinch.

178
00:10:47,200 --> 00:10:49,630
I've already made myself clear.

179
00:10:49,870 --> 00:10:51,750
I know my crimes deserve death.

180
00:10:52,120 --> 00:10:52,910
You two

181
00:10:53,510 --> 00:10:55,510
shouldn't waste any more time on me.

182
00:10:56,608 --> 00:10:58,590
You don't care
about your fake wife and children.

183
00:10:59,080 --> 00:11:00,150
Do you really care nothing

184
00:11:00,480 --> 00:11:01,720
for your real wife and children?

185
00:11:02,880 --> 00:11:04,790
What do you mean by this, Your Highness?

186
00:11:04,800 --> 00:11:06,960
You show no fear
of the extermination of your whole clan.

187
00:11:06,960 --> 00:11:08,600
That goes against basic human nature.

188
00:11:08,600 --> 00:11:09,960
Which leaves only one explanation.

189
00:11:10,360 --> 00:11:12,480
Those people are not your real family.

190
00:11:12,550 --> 00:11:13,750
That's why you remain unmoved.

191
00:11:14,200 --> 00:11:15,440
You're not the real Yu Zao.

192
00:11:16,600 --> 00:11:17,696
I don't know, Your Highness,

193
00:11:17,728 --> 00:11:19,240
why you would make such baseless claims.

194
00:11:19,240 --> 00:11:20,550
You may deny it all you like.

195
00:11:21,320 --> 00:11:22,840
But of all the bribe money you took,

196
00:11:22,880 --> 00:11:23,840
not a single payment

197
00:11:23,840 --> 00:11:26,200
was sent to your wife
or relatives in the capital.

198
00:11:26,750 --> 00:11:27,960
Instead, it all went to Yuzhou.

199
00:11:28,440 --> 00:11:31,000
I imagine someone
very important to you is there.

200
00:11:31,080 --> 00:11:31,960
The real Yu Zao

201
00:11:31,960 --> 00:11:32,976
was ambushed by bandits

202
00:11:32,976 --> 00:11:34,750
on his way to his post two years ago.

203
00:11:34,750 --> 00:11:35,870
Your people killed him,

204
00:11:36,120 --> 00:11:37,630
and you assumed his identity.

205
00:11:37,960 --> 00:11:39,000
For the past two years,

206
00:11:39,000 --> 00:11:40,120
you never returned home,

207
00:11:40,300 --> 00:11:42,550
only kept in touch
with Yu Zao's family through letters.

208
00:11:43,000 --> 00:11:44,080
You and the mastermind

209
00:11:44,080 --> 00:11:45,750
planned, over those two years,

210
00:11:45,870 --> 00:11:47,510
to make full use of the secret prison

211
00:11:47,510 --> 00:11:49,120
and forge enough weapons.

212
00:11:49,488 --> 00:11:50,840
Then you would find an opportunity

213
00:11:50,840 --> 00:11:52,200
to disappear without a trace.

214
00:11:57,200 --> 00:11:58,440
I never expected

215
00:12:00,080 --> 00:12:01,870
you would uncover even this.

216
00:12:02,480 --> 00:12:04,976
If you admit your false identity
and reveal the mastermind,

217
00:12:05,270 --> 00:12:07,270
I will spare your
real wife and children.

218
00:12:09,390 --> 00:12:10,390
What do you say?

219
00:12:11,630 --> 00:12:13,000
Given the situation,

220
00:12:14,080 --> 00:12:16,840
is there a better choice
than what Your Highness has offered?

221
00:12:21,380 --> 00:12:25,060
(Zenan Prefecture)

222
00:12:25,080 --> 00:12:26,496
The imperial decree has been issued.

223
00:12:26,752 --> 00:12:28,512
You will pay
for your crimes with your life.

224
00:12:28,992 --> 00:12:30,720
That will bring this matter to a close.

225
00:12:30,910 --> 00:12:32,440
Your real wife and children

226
00:12:33,200 --> 00:12:34,390
have now been spared.

227
00:12:35,440 --> 00:12:36,670
You can tell us now, can't you?

228
00:12:39,320 --> 00:12:40,870
It was the Duke of Ying.

229
00:12:42,960 --> 00:12:44,390
Twenty years ago,

230
00:12:44,670 --> 00:12:47,440
I joined the army
under the Duke of Ying.

231
00:12:47,840 --> 00:12:49,630
The Duke of Ying
showed me great kindness.

232
00:12:50,440 --> 00:12:51,600
I could not refuse

233
00:12:52,240 --> 00:12:53,790
any of his orders.

234
00:12:54,750 --> 00:12:55,960
The Duke of Ying

235
00:12:57,360 --> 00:12:58,670
is in Anlan now?

236
00:13:01,000 --> 00:13:02,720
Something has happened
to the Duke of Ying.

237
00:13:03,600 --> 00:13:06,030
He had close dealings
with a Hu merchant.

238
00:13:06,790 --> 00:13:07,600
In the past,

239
00:13:07,750 --> 00:13:09,390
he secretly obtained poisons

240
00:13:09,480 --> 00:13:11,360
through that merchant.

241
00:13:12,480 --> 00:13:14,670
The merchant gained leverage over him

242
00:13:14,670 --> 00:13:16,600
and became increasingly overbearing.

243
00:13:17,150 --> 00:13:20,080
The Duke of Ying decided to silence him.

244
00:13:21,030 --> 00:13:22,030
Unexpectedly,

245
00:13:22,030 --> 00:13:25,120
the merchant poisoned
the Duke of Ying and escaped.

246
00:13:26,510 --> 00:13:28,030
After being poisoned, the Duke of Ying

247
00:13:28,550 --> 00:13:30,670
could barely eat anything.

248
00:13:31,080 --> 00:13:32,670
His insides burned with unbearable pain,

249
00:13:32,910 --> 00:13:34,150
leaving him in constant agony.

250
00:13:35,840 --> 00:13:37,150
After that,

251
00:13:37,840 --> 00:13:39,360
his whereabouts became unknown.

252
00:13:43,320 --> 00:13:44,240
My fellow citizens,

253
00:13:44,340 --> 00:13:46,710
I am the Deputy Chief Justice
of the Court of Judicial Review.

254
00:13:46,720 --> 00:13:47,790
By order of the court,

255
00:13:48,256 --> 00:13:50,352
I have come to resolve
the secret prison case.

256
00:13:50,440 --> 00:13:51,910
The culprit impersonated Yu Zao,

257
00:13:52,000 --> 00:13:54,200
and all his accomplices
have been arrested.

258
00:13:54,784 --> 00:13:55,630
The secret prison

259
00:13:56,750 --> 00:13:58,000
has been completely destroyed.

260
00:13:58,240 --> 00:14:00,480
The court is fully aware
of the suffering you have endured.

261
00:14:01,120 --> 00:14:02,750
His Majesty is deeply grieved as well.

262
00:14:03,184 --> 00:14:04,200
By His Majesty's decree,

263
00:14:04,896 --> 00:14:06,480
all victims of the secret prison case

264
00:14:06,720 --> 00:14:07,550
and their families

265
00:14:08,360 --> 00:14:09,390
will receive relief.

266
00:14:09,504 --> 00:14:11,630
His Majesty has appointed
Commandery Princess Zhaoning

267
00:14:11,840 --> 00:14:13,030
to oversee these arrangements.

268
00:14:18,240 --> 00:14:18,870
Everyone,

269
00:14:19,232 --> 00:14:21,104
those who suffered
in the secret prison case

270
00:14:22,080 --> 00:14:23,320
and lost a family member,

271
00:14:23,408 --> 00:14:24,840
please proceed to the green banner.

272
00:14:25,320 --> 00:14:27,200
Each person
will receive 500 copper coins

273
00:14:27,200 --> 00:14:28,000
and 25 kg of rice.

274
00:14:28,010 --> 00:14:29,560
The elderly, the weak,
ladies, and kids

275
00:14:29,570 --> 00:14:30,820
may proceed to the yellow banner.

276
00:14:30,840 --> 00:14:32,990
Each person will receive
an additional 6.25 kg of millet.

277
00:14:33,000 --> 00:14:34,440
Those who are ill or injured

278
00:14:34,670 --> 00:14:35,910
may proceed to the red banner.

279
00:14:36,256 --> 00:14:37,960
A physician will examine you personally.

280
00:14:38,032 --> 00:14:39,370
Anyone wishing to file a complaint

281
00:14:39,390 --> 00:14:40,630
may go to the white banner.

282
00:14:40,800 --> 00:14:42,630
A legal clerk
will help prepare your petition.

283
00:14:43,150 --> 00:14:44,150
Hot soup and rice cakes

284
00:14:44,150 --> 00:14:45,600
have been prepared at every station.

285
00:14:45,840 --> 00:14:47,150
Please help yourselves.

286
00:14:47,270 --> 00:14:49,630
- Thank You, Your Majesty!
- Thank You, Your Majesty!

287
00:14:50,390 --> 00:14:51,360
Thank You, Your Majesty!

288
00:14:51,630 --> 00:14:53,984
- Thank you, Your Highness!
- Thank you, Your Highness!

289
00:14:54,000 --> 00:14:55,120
Thank you, Your Highness!

290
00:14:55,440 --> 00:14:56,240
Please, rise.

291
00:14:56,870 --> 00:14:57,390
Please rise.

292
00:14:57,390 --> 00:14:58,150
Please, rise.

293
00:14:58,150 --> 00:14:59,200
Everyone, please rise.

294
00:14:59,472 --> 00:15:00,480
Please, all of you, rise.

295
00:15:00,480 --> 00:15:01,080
Please rise.

296
00:15:01,480 --> 00:15:02,600
Thank you, Your Highness.

297
00:15:02,800 --> 00:15:03,720
Go collect your relief.

298
00:15:04,720 --> 00:15:05,910
Thank you, Your Highness.

299
00:15:07,030 --> 00:15:08,030
Here, take it slow.

300
00:15:17,550 --> 00:15:19,320
Your Highness,
by the Crown Prince's order,

301
00:15:19,720 --> 00:15:20,660
the front of this stele

302
00:15:20,704 --> 00:15:22,360
is engraved
with the Relief Proclamation.

303
00:15:22,496 --> 00:15:24,550
Anyone left alone
because of official injustice

304
00:15:24,768 --> 00:15:26,576
will receive 50 copper coins each month.

305
00:15:27,088 --> 00:15:28,360
If a prisoner dies of illness,

306
00:15:28,360 --> 00:15:30,240
(Relief Proclamation)
the body must be examined

307
00:15:30,240 --> 00:15:31,230
by the coroner,
the family, and local elders.

308
00:15:31,248 --> 00:15:33,184
The back of the stele bears
the Collective Accountability Order.

309
00:15:33,216 --> 00:15:35,230
If three wrongful imprisonments
occur within a prefecture,

310
00:15:35,240 --> 00:15:36,752
the prefect will be branded and exiled.

311
00:15:36,760 --> 00:15:37,830
If there are more than five,

312
00:15:37,840 --> 00:15:39,990
their entire clan
will be permanently barred from office.

313
00:15:40,016 --> 00:15:41,730
The secret prison case
has now been solved.

314
00:15:41,750 --> 00:15:43,630
The Crown Prince
deserves some credit as well.

315
00:15:43,960 --> 00:15:45,360
What did the Crown Prince give you

316
00:15:45,696 --> 00:15:47,120
to make you keep taking his side?

317
00:15:47,600 --> 00:15:49,600
The Crown Prince
is always helping Your Highness.

318
00:15:49,600 --> 00:15:51,580
I don't need any favors
from him to take his side.

319
00:15:51,630 --> 00:15:54,360
If Your Highness and the Crown Prince
become husband and wife

320
00:15:54,360 --> 00:15:55,710
and govern the East Palace together,

321
00:15:55,720 --> 00:15:57,520
it would truly
be a blessing for the people.

322
00:15:58,790 --> 00:16:00,670
Are you really no longer considering

323
00:16:00,670 --> 00:16:02,200
marrying the Crown Prince?

324
00:16:02,320 --> 00:16:03,390
Once you enter the palace,

325
00:16:04,224 --> 00:16:05,790
there can be no room for a soft heart.

326
00:16:49,136 --> 00:16:50,048
Your Highness,

327
00:16:50,050 --> 00:16:52,480
Crown Prince's carriage
has been following us from a distance.

328
00:16:52,480 --> 00:16:53,510
He hasn't come any closer.

329
00:16:56,200 --> 00:16:57,080
Just ignore him.

330
00:17:34,640 --> 00:17:36,880
♪A wall that collapses at a single push♪

331
00:17:38,210 --> 00:17:40,460
♪Frost that melts at a single smile♪

332
00:17:41,780 --> 00:17:47,060
♪How can you be this wonderful♪

333
00:17:48,990 --> 00:17:51,930
♪I've hidden so many words♪

334
00:17:52,550 --> 00:17:55,350
♪Too reluctant to tell you♪

335
00:17:56,220 --> 00:18:03,190
♪So never uncover♪

336
00:18:03,380 --> 00:18:05,740
♪The sand that slips away
with one grasp♪

337
00:18:06,870 --> 00:18:09,600
♪The flower that withers
after one bloom♪

338
00:18:10,560 --> 00:18:15,900
♪Silently buried deep inside my heart♪

339
00:18:17,660 --> 00:18:20,480
♪Every answer I gave♪

340
00:18:21,280 --> 00:18:24,130
♪Was both bittersweet and absurd♪

341
00:18:24,920 --> 00:18:28,290
♪Hiding my tear-filled eyes
when I hurt you♪

342
00:18:29,550 --> 00:18:30,720
You truly are

343
00:18:30,752 --> 00:18:32,240
a fairy beneath the Jade Terrace moon,

344
00:18:32,400 --> 00:18:33,720
standing gracefully in the breeze.

345
00:18:44,680 --> 00:18:46,110
And you

346
00:18:46,310 --> 00:18:48,790
are no different from a snake
that won't leave my side.

347
00:18:49,400 --> 00:18:50,110
That's quite true.

348
00:18:50,256 --> 00:18:51,510
I do tend to cling to people.

349
00:18:53,296 --> 00:18:54,960
The secret prison case in Zenan District

350
00:18:55,100 --> 00:18:56,400
was brought to a successful close

351
00:18:56,560 --> 00:18:57,750
thanks to your brilliant plan.

352
00:18:59,350 --> 00:19:01,240
Though you keep saying
it's for mutual benefit,

353
00:19:01,310 --> 00:19:02,944
you've also brought justice
to the people

354
00:19:02,992 --> 00:19:04,070
with the greatest care.

355
00:19:05,510 --> 00:19:06,680
If Bu Shulin

356
00:19:06,790 --> 00:19:08,512
were not the heir
of the Marquis of Shunan,

357
00:19:09,030 --> 00:19:10,640
I wouldn't have gotten involved

358
00:19:10,640 --> 00:19:11,720
from the very beginning.

359
00:19:16,550 --> 00:19:17,690
Then why don't we join forces

360
00:19:18,720 --> 00:19:20,830
to bring down the entire
Marquis of Shunan's Manor

361
00:19:21,010 --> 00:19:22,830
and absorb them all
into the Northwest Army?

362
00:19:23,264 --> 00:19:24,160
What do you think?

363
00:19:28,720 --> 00:19:29,200
See?

364
00:19:29,960 --> 00:19:32,350
Why must you make yourself
sound so heartless?

365
00:19:33,920 --> 00:19:34,640
Your Highness,

366
00:19:35,790 --> 00:19:36,790
no matter what you say,

367
00:19:38,270 --> 00:19:39,270
this engagement

368
00:19:39,680 --> 00:19:41,070
must be broken.

369
00:19:57,472 --> 00:19:58,640
You are bullying me again.

370
00:20:17,970 --> 00:20:21,040
♪Light as a dream, time drifts by♪

371
00:20:22,110 --> 00:20:24,720
♪Pushing the sea
of stars to flow across♪

372
00:20:26,160 --> 00:20:28,740
♪Flowers wilt and bloom again♪

373
00:20:29,190 --> 00:20:31,530
♪In an endless cycle♪

374
00:20:34,170 --> 00:20:37,090
♪Whispers beneath the moon♪

375
00:20:37,630 --> 00:20:40,740
♪Slowly spread across the branches♪

376
00:20:41,540 --> 00:20:43,410
♪Longing is so beautiful♪

377
00:20:43,650 --> 00:20:48,090
♪How many still wander
as they did in their youth?♪

378
00:20:50,050 --> 00:20:52,720
♪Amidst the flickering lights♪

379
00:20:54,080 --> 00:20:56,790
♪Alone for several autumns♪

380
00:20:58,180 --> 00:21:00,630
♪How to choose the one♪

381
00:21:01,010 --> 00:21:04,570
♪To be with forever?♪

382
00:21:05,650 --> 00:21:08,940
♪When I gaze upon you♪

383
00:21:09,570 --> 00:21:12,910
♪Flower petals twirl gently in my heart♪

384
00:21:13,510 --> 00:21:14,970
♪Gracefully♪

385
00:21:15,680 --> 00:21:20,740
♪For all eternity♪

386
00:21:21,440 --> 00:21:23,000
It doesn't matter if some things

387
00:21:23,500 --> 00:21:24,736
take a little longer.

388
00:21:24,832 --> 00:21:28,020
♪Quietly reflect in your sparkling eyes♪

389
00:21:28,830 --> 00:21:29,680
I'm willing to wait.

390
00:21:29,680 --> 00:21:31,930
♪Scattered red petals fall like rain♪

391
00:21:32,390 --> 00:21:36,230
♪It's a wonderful time in the world♪

392
00:21:37,170 --> 00:21:40,010
♪Bits of worries and sorrows♪

393
00:21:40,410 --> 00:21:44,020
♪Are gently gathered
into your elegant sleeves♪

394
00:21:45,130 --> 00:21:47,890
♪Gradually, on the misty path♪

395
00:21:48,390 --> 00:21:52,190
♪Not a trace of sorrow can be found♪

396
00:21:58,940 --> 00:22:01,020
(Zenan Post Station)

397
00:22:07,400 --> 00:22:08,310
Your Highness, look.

398
00:22:12,640 --> 00:22:14,240
I'd like to travel with you.

399
00:22:14,380 --> 00:22:16,160
We can look after each other
along the way.

400
00:22:16,176 --> 00:22:16,820
What do you say?

401
00:22:16,848 --> 00:22:17,570
I don't need that.

402
00:22:23,960 --> 00:22:24,920
But I do.

403
00:22:31,640 --> 00:22:33,160
Don't you want to know

404
00:22:33,580 --> 00:22:35,310
the truth behind
Consort Liang's poisoning?

405
00:22:36,790 --> 00:22:38,350
Before Yu Zao was executed, he told me

406
00:22:38,496 --> 00:22:40,350
the mastermind
behind the secret prison case

407
00:22:40,350 --> 00:22:41,310
was the Duke of Ying.

408
00:22:41,680 --> 00:22:43,920
He also bought poison
from the merchant many times.

409
00:22:43,984 --> 00:22:45,410
After committing so many evil deeds,

410
00:22:45,420 --> 00:22:46,920
he was poisoned by that very merchant.

411
00:22:46,930 --> 00:22:49,216
He should now be hiding
somewhere in the imperial capital.

412
00:22:50,200 --> 00:22:51,510
You're exceptionally perceptive.

413
00:22:51,510 --> 00:22:53,030
I'd like to join forces
with you again

414
00:22:53,030 --> 00:22:54,030
to find his whereabouts.

415
00:22:58,020 --> 00:22:59,776
This has nothing to do
with our engagement.

416
00:23:00,640 --> 00:23:01,480
We'll work together

417
00:23:01,960 --> 00:23:03,200
only to find the real culprit.

418
00:23:03,880 --> 00:23:04,400
Very well.

419
00:23:05,270 --> 00:23:06,030
I agree.

420
00:23:36,160 --> 00:23:37,104
Return to the palace.

421
00:23:42,220 --> 00:23:45,420
(Residence of the Heir
of the Marquis of Shunan)

422
00:23:49,920 --> 00:23:51,424
You were injured in the black prison,

423
00:23:51,424 --> 00:23:52,690
so you need to rest and recover.

424
00:23:52,720 --> 00:23:54,030
Avoid cold and spicy foods.

425
00:23:54,480 --> 00:23:55,640
I still can't eat that.

426
00:23:56,030 --> 00:23:57,510
Then... then take a look at this.

427
00:23:57,510 --> 00:23:59,280
Shouldn't I
be eating something nourishing?

428
00:24:00,720 --> 00:24:02,270
You should listen to Physician Xie.

429
00:24:05,350 --> 00:24:06,440
I was only

430
00:24:06,440 --> 00:24:09,480
trying to appear a little
more delicate before Physician Xie

431
00:24:09,480 --> 00:24:10,640
so he would take pity on me.

432
00:24:11,540 --> 00:24:13,110
- Seeing him in person today.
- Please.

433
00:24:13,110 --> 00:24:15,880
Physician Xie truly has the grace
of a jade-like immortal.

434
00:24:17,240 --> 00:24:19,960
Then how does Physician Xie
compare to Vice Minister Cui?

435
00:24:21,240 --> 00:24:23,680
Physician Xie is as gentle
and refined as jade.

436
00:24:23,880 --> 00:24:24,720
As for Cui Jinbai,

437
00:24:24,720 --> 00:24:26,830
he's nothing but a dull,
useless lump of stone.

438
00:24:26,830 --> 00:24:27,640
How can jade

439
00:24:27,640 --> 00:24:28,960
be compared to stone?

440
00:24:29,110 --> 00:24:30,790
Young Master, you do love to joke.

441
00:24:31,070 --> 00:24:32,070
I mean every word.

442
00:24:32,200 --> 00:24:33,030
I'll take my leave.

443
00:24:41,264 --> 00:24:42,880
I have matters to attend to at home.

444
00:24:43,100 --> 00:24:44,000
I'll be going as well.

445
00:24:44,112 --> 00:24:45,830
- I'll come see you another day.
- Xihe...

446
00:24:52,030 --> 00:24:53,270
What sweet words you have.

447
00:24:53,328 --> 00:24:54,480
Looks like you've recovered.

448
00:24:55,830 --> 00:24:57,000
Just now,

449
00:24:57,000 --> 00:24:58,720
I was only complimenting our guest.

450
00:24:58,720 --> 00:25:00,440
I didn't mean to put you down.

451
00:25:00,440 --> 00:25:01,680
I'm glad you're feeling better.

452
00:25:07,160 --> 00:25:08,830
Jin Shan, look at him.

453
00:25:08,830 --> 00:25:10,000
Such a terrible temper.

454
00:25:12,480 --> 00:25:13,480
Go see him off.

455
00:25:13,880 --> 00:25:14,400
Yes.

456
00:25:29,590 --> 00:25:30,270
Young Master,

457
00:25:30,352 --> 00:25:32,384
I've escorted
Vice Minister Cui to his carriage.

458
00:25:32,448 --> 00:25:34,416
If he's gone, then he's gone.
No need to tell me.

459
00:25:37,000 --> 00:25:37,640
Jin Shan,

460
00:25:38,070 --> 00:25:39,880
where's that box from Shiweizhai?

461
00:25:39,904 --> 00:25:41,000
The one carved with peonies?

462
00:25:41,000 --> 00:25:42,480
That's the one. Go bring it to me.

463
00:25:42,960 --> 00:25:44,880
I saw Vice Minister Cui was quite upset,

464
00:25:44,880 --> 00:25:46,270
so I already gave it to him.

465
00:25:48,000 --> 00:25:49,480
Who told you to give it to him?

466
00:25:49,640 --> 00:25:51,110
Who told you to give it to him?

467
00:25:51,110 --> 00:25:52,750
Why are you so worked up, Young Master?

468
00:25:52,750 --> 00:25:54,030
It's only a box of pastries.

469
00:26:08,720 --> 00:26:09,790
Stone Cui!

470
00:26:14,790 --> 00:26:15,480
Stone Cui!

471
00:26:16,830 --> 00:26:17,440
Stone Cui!

472
00:26:23,960 --> 00:26:25,790
I gave you the wrong box of pastries.

473
00:26:27,880 --> 00:26:29,270
Then who was it meant for?

474
00:26:30,272 --> 00:26:32,240
Wang Sanlang
of the Marquis of Zhenbei's Manor.

475
00:26:36,830 --> 00:26:38,350
You're giving him something like this?

476
00:26:39,240 --> 00:26:40,960
You two must be very close.

477
00:26:51,480 --> 00:26:52,680
We're just drinking buddies.

478
00:26:53,168 --> 00:26:55,400
I promised him long ago.
I couldn't go back on my word.

479
00:26:55,400 --> 00:26:56,330
Don't take it to heart.

480
00:26:56,480 --> 00:26:57,960
I'll give you a new box another day.

481
00:27:11,720 --> 00:27:14,480
I've given instructions regarding
Your Highness and the Crown Prince's

482
00:27:14,576 --> 00:27:15,750
search for the Duke of Ying.

483
00:27:16,080 --> 00:27:17,750
Every apothecary
in the imperial capital,

484
00:27:17,960 --> 00:27:19,750
if anyone tries to buy antidotes,

485
00:27:19,750 --> 00:27:20,720
I'll know about it.

486
00:27:20,752 --> 00:27:22,864
I'll have to trouble
Physician Xie again this time.

487
00:27:22,920 --> 00:27:24,490
No need to be so polite, Your Highness.

488
00:27:24,510 --> 00:27:26,110
Your wisdom and decisiveness

489
00:27:26,790 --> 00:27:27,880
have earned my admiration.

490
00:27:28,550 --> 00:27:29,830
To have you as a friend

491
00:27:29,830 --> 00:27:30,830
is my great fortune.

492
00:27:31,270 --> 00:27:32,440
You flatter me, Physician Xie.

493
00:27:33,310 --> 00:27:35,510
Actually, there's something
I've always wondered.

494
00:27:36,110 --> 00:27:37,350
Back then, Physician Xie,

495
00:27:37,350 --> 00:27:39,640
why did you sever ties
with the Duke of Xie,

496
00:27:40,000 --> 00:27:42,240
give up your title,
and become a physician?

497
00:27:48,000 --> 00:27:49,350
The reason I studied medicine

498
00:27:49,640 --> 00:27:50,720
was because of my mother.

499
00:27:50,720 --> 00:27:53,250
She died from a prescription
mistakenly written by a physician.

500
00:27:53,640 --> 00:27:55,000
The medicine wasn't poisonous,

501
00:27:55,216 --> 00:27:56,540
but it wasn't the right treatment.

502
00:27:57,264 --> 00:27:58,680
My mother took it for three years

503
00:27:58,864 --> 00:27:59,960
and died without a cure.

504
00:28:00,550 --> 00:28:01,550
And all of it

505
00:28:02,480 --> 00:28:04,240
was arranged by the man I called father,

506
00:28:04,750 --> 00:28:06,070
the Duke of Xie.

507
00:28:06,750 --> 00:28:08,640
Why was the Duke of Xie so heartless?

508
00:28:09,000 --> 00:28:10,680
He had someone he loved in his youth.

509
00:28:11,270 --> 00:28:13,350
To marry again,
he murdered his first wife

510
00:28:13,960 --> 00:28:15,030
after careful planning.

511
00:28:15,152 --> 00:28:16,830
Yet he pretended
to be a devoted husband,

512
00:28:16,830 --> 00:28:18,140
showing endless care and concern.

513
00:28:18,680 --> 00:28:19,920
That was why

514
00:28:20,816 --> 00:28:23,640
I couldn't bear to stay in the
Duke of Xie's Manor another moment.

515
00:28:28,912 --> 00:28:31,000
Being able to speak honestly
with Your Highness today

516
00:28:31,072 --> 00:28:33,040
has eased the burden
I've carried in my heart.

517
00:28:33,200 --> 00:28:34,070
I'm truly grateful.

518
00:28:34,440 --> 00:28:35,790
Just remember, Physician Xie,

519
00:28:36,030 --> 00:28:37,310
we are true friends.

520
00:28:37,880 --> 00:28:39,640
If you ever face any hardship,

521
00:28:40,000 --> 00:28:41,640
I'll do everything I can to help.

522
00:28:46,540 --> 00:28:47,580
(Baicao Herb House)

523
00:28:47,590 --> 00:28:49,550
Those people did indeed buy antidotes.

524
00:28:50,400 --> 00:28:51,790
Do you know who they are?

525
00:28:54,030 --> 00:28:54,960
Speak at once.

526
00:28:55,550 --> 00:28:57,750
They were from the Duke of Xie's Manor.

527
00:29:04,790 --> 00:29:05,400
Young Master,

528
00:29:06,030 --> 00:29:07,000
should we

529
00:29:07,216 --> 00:29:09,550
inform the Crown Prince
and Commandery Princess first?

530
00:29:09,830 --> 00:29:10,270
No.

531
00:29:10,750 --> 00:29:11,510
I'll go myself.

532
00:29:12,160 --> 00:29:13,136
Three days from now,

533
00:29:13,550 --> 00:29:14,480
if I haven't returned,

534
00:29:15,200 --> 00:29:17,440
inform the Crown Prince
and Commandery Princess Zhaoning.

535
00:29:17,960 --> 00:29:18,440
Yes.

536
00:29:21,980 --> 00:29:23,580
(Duke of Wei's Manor)

537
00:29:24,270 --> 00:29:25,070
Your Highness,

538
00:29:26,368 --> 00:29:28,144
something has happened to Physician Xie.

539
00:29:35,110 --> 00:29:38,000
Duke of Xie dared not invite a renowned
physician to treat Duke of Ying,

540
00:29:38,016 --> 00:29:40,240
so he could only search
the city's apothecaries in secret

541
00:29:40,240 --> 00:29:41,400
for antidotal herbs.

542
00:29:41,400 --> 00:29:41,960
Your Highness,

543
00:29:42,440 --> 00:29:43,480
what if

544
00:29:43,480 --> 00:29:44,920
the Duke of Xie denies it?

545
00:29:48,720 --> 00:29:49,310
Your Highness,

546
00:29:49,552 --> 00:29:51,790
the message has already
been sent to the Crown Prince.

547
00:29:52,030 --> 00:29:52,790
His Highness said

548
00:29:52,790 --> 00:29:54,200
everything is up to Your Highness.

549
00:29:54,310 --> 00:29:55,030
How wonderful.

550
00:29:55,310 --> 00:29:58,030
Crown Prince respects Your Highness
from the bottom of his heart.

551
00:29:58,200 --> 00:29:59,350
Your Highness's decisions

552
00:29:59,440 --> 00:30:02,030
have always had
the Crown Prince's full support.

553
00:30:02,030 --> 00:30:03,110
You two

554
00:30:03,500 --> 00:30:05,480
never miss a chance
to speak for the Crown Prince.

555
00:30:16,260 --> 00:30:18,300
(Duke of Xie's Manor)

556
00:30:18,400 --> 00:30:20,970
Your Highness, my lady says she hasn't
been feeling well lately

557
00:30:20,976 --> 00:30:22,470
and is unable to receive Your Highness.

558
00:30:22,480 --> 00:30:23,350
Once she has recovered,

559
00:30:23,350 --> 00:30:25,008
she'll send
Your Highness an invitation.

560
00:30:28,920 --> 00:30:30,160
Your Highness's cat ran off.

561
00:30:31,590 --> 00:30:33,090
- What? Your Highness...
- Catch it!

562
00:30:33,104 --> 00:30:34,624
Having you announce my arrival

563
00:30:34,830 --> 00:30:36,590
was merely to show her some courtesy.

564
00:30:41,488 --> 00:30:42,640
What are you waiting for?

565
00:30:42,640 --> 00:30:43,480
Go help!

566
00:30:48,510 --> 00:30:49,960
It's over there! Hurry!

567
00:30:59,456 --> 00:31:00,768
(It smells like medicine.)

568
00:31:04,790 --> 00:31:05,510
To the south.

569
00:31:06,440 --> 00:31:08,960
Greetings, Commandery Princess Zhaoning.

570
00:31:11,220 --> 00:31:12,500
(Duke of Xie's Manor)

571
00:31:12,540 --> 00:31:14,900
(Yuan, Wife of the Duke of Xie)

572
00:31:14,920 --> 00:31:16,550
This is the Duke of Xie's Manor.

573
00:31:17,510 --> 00:31:19,310
How can Your Highness
search it so openly?

574
00:31:19,550 --> 00:31:20,880
My cat went missing here.

575
00:31:21,008 --> 00:31:22,290
Naturally, I have to look for it.

576
00:31:23,830 --> 00:31:24,440
Mo Yu.

577
00:31:26,960 --> 00:31:27,640
How dare you!

578
00:31:29,640 --> 00:31:31,110
Commandery Princess Zhaoning,

579
00:31:32,640 --> 00:31:34,880
you certainly have some nerve.

580
00:31:35,960 --> 00:31:36,720
Duke.

581
00:31:39,140 --> 00:31:40,660
(Duke of Xie)
Your Highness,

582
00:31:40,680 --> 00:31:43,030
do you take the imperial capital
for the northwest?

583
00:31:43,200 --> 00:31:45,270
Neither princes nor princesses

584
00:31:45,550 --> 00:31:48,310
would dare behave with such arrogance.

585
00:31:50,920 --> 00:31:52,000
Greetings, Duke of Xie.

586
00:31:53,720 --> 00:31:55,750
I'm only looking for my cat.

587
00:31:57,750 --> 00:31:58,480
Guards!

588
00:32:05,550 --> 00:32:06,160
Mo Yuan.

589
00:32:06,160 --> 00:32:08,540
(Duke of Xie's Manor)

590
00:32:18,640 --> 00:32:20,200
His Majesty has granted me 500 guards.

591
00:32:21,350 --> 00:32:22,960
The Duke's guards

592
00:32:22,960 --> 00:32:24,110
number only forty or fifty.

593
00:32:24,350 --> 00:32:26,400
Do you truly intend
to stand against me, Duke?

594
00:32:26,790 --> 00:32:28,240
I will never allow you

595
00:32:28,240 --> 00:32:29,664
to disgrace the Duke of Xie's Manor.

596
00:32:34,768 --> 00:32:36,510
The Duke of Xie's Manor
is heavily guarded.

597
00:32:36,510 --> 00:32:37,720
If we remain at a standoff,

598
00:32:37,960 --> 00:32:39,440
Physician Xie will be put in danger.

599
00:32:39,920 --> 00:32:41,440
We should make this matter bigger

600
00:32:41,450 --> 00:32:43,060
and bring
the Prefecture of Jingzhao here.

601
00:32:43,070 --> 00:32:44,770
We'll use their authority
to our advantage.

602
00:32:44,784 --> 00:32:45,920
Please calm down, both of you.

603
00:32:45,920 --> 00:32:48,128
(Gathering Auspiciousness and Virtue)
Please calm down!

604
00:32:48,200 --> 00:32:48,830
Prefect Zhang,

605
00:32:49,568 --> 00:32:51,680
Commandery Princess Zhaoning
is abusing her authority

606
00:32:51,920 --> 00:32:53,590
and insists on searching my manor.

607
00:32:54,510 --> 00:32:55,160
Prefect Zhang,

608
00:32:55,696 --> 00:32:57,880
the golden plaque bestowed
by His Majesty is missing.

609
00:32:58,110 --> 00:33:00,790
The Duke of Xie and his wife
refuse to return it.

610
00:33:01,000 --> 00:33:02,400
What utter nonsense!

611
00:33:03,590 --> 00:33:05,790
Your Highness, do you have any evidence?

612
00:33:06,016 --> 00:33:07,590
We'll have our evidence once we find it.

613
00:33:10,464 --> 00:33:11,750
Do you realize, Your Highness,

614
00:33:11,920 --> 00:33:14,440
that if the golden plaque is not
in the Duke of Xie's Manor,

615
00:33:14,510 --> 00:33:16,880
you will be caned according to the law?

616
00:33:17,070 --> 00:33:20,440
I'm certain the golden plaque
is in the Duke of Xie's Manor.

617
00:33:26,048 --> 00:33:26,848
Duke of Xie,

618
00:33:26,848 --> 00:33:29,270
the loss of the golden plaque
is a matter of great importance.

619
00:33:29,270 --> 00:33:30,680
I dare not take it lightly.

620
00:33:30,680 --> 00:33:31,310
Why not

621
00:33:31,310 --> 00:33:34,070
allow me to bring two guards

622
00:33:34,070 --> 00:33:35,000
to conduct a search?

623
00:33:35,200 --> 00:33:35,590
You...

624
00:33:36,030 --> 00:33:37,000
Thank you, Prefect Zhang.

625
00:33:46,200 --> 00:33:47,310
This is the last room.

626
00:33:53,904 --> 00:33:55,030
Your Highness, please stop.

627
00:33:55,520 --> 00:33:57,110
This is the Xie family ancestral hall.

628
00:33:57,350 --> 00:33:59,240
Outsiders are not permitted inside.

629
00:34:01,000 --> 00:34:01,550
Your Highness,

630
00:34:01,880 --> 00:34:05,030
this hall enshrines
our ancestors' spirit tablets.

631
00:34:05,030 --> 00:34:06,640
Those outside the family
should not enter.

632
00:34:06,640 --> 00:34:08,360
Perhaps we should leave it at that.

633
00:34:09,110 --> 00:34:10,150
Precisely because of that,

634
00:34:10,670 --> 00:34:12,840
this is the most concealed place.

635
00:34:14,710 --> 00:34:17,070
Are you trying to disturb the peace

636
00:34:17,070 --> 00:34:18,070
of my Xie ancestors?

637
00:34:18,230 --> 00:34:19,550
If it's not found here,

638
00:34:19,760 --> 00:34:21,480
I'll personally apologize

639
00:34:21,480 --> 00:34:23,232
before the Xie family's
ancestral tablets.

640
00:34:33,820 --> 00:34:35,340
(Xie Family Ancestral Hall)

641
00:34:38,740 --> 00:34:42,500
(Spirit Tablets
of the Xie Family Ancestors)

642
00:34:43,400 --> 00:34:44,110
My goodness!

643
00:34:50,460 --> 00:34:53,140
(Spirit Tablets
of the Xie Family Ancestors)

644
00:34:54,500 --> 00:34:56,060
(Ning)

645
00:34:56,800 --> 00:34:57,760
The golden plaque!

646
00:34:58,190 --> 00:34:58,960
That's impossible!

647
00:34:58,960 --> 00:35:01,800
If the Duke of Xie refuses to accept
this, then appeal to His Majesty.

648
00:35:04,640 --> 00:35:06,320
Once we're inside
the Duke of Xie's Manor,

649
00:35:06,576 --> 00:35:08,432
it'll be your turn
to make your contribution.

650
00:35:09,776 --> 00:35:11,232
(Ning)
We need to lure the Duke of Xie

651
00:35:11,232 --> 00:35:12,630
out of his manor,

652
00:35:12,630 --> 00:35:14,760
so the Crown Prince
can find the Duke of Ying

653
00:35:14,760 --> 00:35:15,760
and rescue Xie Yunhuai.

654
00:35:16,510 --> 00:35:17,840
Use this to lure Du Huo.

655
00:35:19,550 --> 00:35:20,400
(To the south.)

656
00:35:21,000 --> 00:35:21,550
Mo Yu.

657
00:35:22,000 --> 00:35:22,630
How dare you!

658
00:35:24,700 --> 00:35:26,460
(Xie Family Ancestral Hall)

659
00:35:35,260 --> 00:35:37,740
(Xie Family Ancestral Hall)

660
00:35:37,740 --> 00:35:40,140
(Sixian Hall)

661
00:35:40,880 --> 00:35:41,510
Your Highness,

662
00:35:41,630 --> 00:35:43,760
Commandery Princess suspects the Duke
of Xie's Manor has a secret passage.

663
00:35:43,808 --> 00:35:45,530
To make it easier
to move the Duke of Ying,

664
00:35:45,550 --> 00:35:47,070
it shouldn't have only one exit.

665
00:35:47,070 --> 00:35:48,496
It must connect to a second exit.

666
00:35:49,880 --> 00:35:51,360
Tian Yuan, bring me the map.

667
00:35:59,030 --> 00:36:01,550
(The Imperial Palace)
A single passage can have many exits.

668
00:36:01,568 --> 00:36:03,150
They're built by a waterside pavilion,

669
00:36:03,150 --> 00:36:04,880
leading directly to the underground
waterway for an easy escape.

670
00:36:04,890 --> 00:36:06,960
On the southeastern side
of the Duke of Xie's Manor,

671
00:36:06,976 --> 00:36:07,984
there is indeed a river.

672
00:36:08,360 --> 00:36:10,480
But there's only a bare dock.

673
00:36:10,710 --> 00:36:11,920
There isn't a single building.

674
00:36:11,920 --> 00:36:13,500
It's nothing but the riverbed and rocks.

675
00:36:13,550 --> 00:36:14,710
How could there be an exit?

676
00:36:15,230 --> 00:36:17,070
I once read
in the military defense records

677
00:36:17,630 --> 00:36:18,360
that an exit

678
00:36:18,670 --> 00:36:20,920
could be disguised as a mooring post.

679
00:36:21,550 --> 00:36:22,480
On the surface,

680
00:36:23,056 --> 00:36:24,840
it looks just like
any other mooring post.

681
00:36:25,230 --> 00:36:26,400
But it's actually hollow,

682
00:36:26,510 --> 00:36:27,872
with a hidden mechanism inside.

683
00:36:28,400 --> 00:36:29,030
Tian Yuan,

684
00:36:29,800 --> 00:36:32,070
bring me twenty guards
who are skilled swimmers.

685
00:36:32,630 --> 00:36:34,550
There must be a secret passage
beneath the dock.

686
00:36:34,550 --> 00:36:35,328
(Dock)

687
00:36:36,150 --> 00:36:36,880
Your Majesty,

688
00:36:37,070 --> 00:36:38,230
throughout the realm,

689
00:36:38,360 --> 00:36:39,920
only the Commandery Princess

690
00:36:39,920 --> 00:36:41,590
possesses this imperial golden plaque.

691
00:36:41,590 --> 00:36:43,280
Even if I stole it, it would be useless.

692
00:36:43,400 --> 00:36:45,760
You're mistaken, Duke of Xie.

693
00:36:45,840 --> 00:36:47,480
Once someone leaves
the imperial capital,

694
00:36:47,920 --> 00:36:50,880
local officials recognize
only the imperial golden plaque.

695
00:36:50,880 --> 00:36:53,440
Seeing it is the same
as seeing His Majesty himself.

696
00:36:53,670 --> 00:36:55,550
They need only obey.

697
00:36:56,150 --> 00:36:59,088
Your Majesty, the Xie family has served
with distinction for generations.

698
00:36:59,320 --> 00:37:01,030
I have never
harbored disloyal intentions.

699
00:37:01,150 --> 00:37:03,440
Your heart lies within your own body.

700
00:37:04,440 --> 00:37:06,070
How could His Majesty know

701
00:37:06,070 --> 00:37:08,320
whether you harbor disloyal intentions?

702
00:37:08,510 --> 00:37:11,030
Minister Tao is unmatched
in the art of debate.

703
00:37:11,030 --> 00:37:13,360
I can't outargue you,

704
00:37:14,190 --> 00:37:17,150
but I will never allow
such slander and false accusations.

705
00:37:25,030 --> 00:37:25,670
Who's there?

706
00:38:07,190 --> 00:38:09,070
Your Highness?

707
00:38:09,400 --> 00:38:10,880
The Duke of Ying is gravely ill.

708
00:38:11,840 --> 00:38:13,550
How can you recover

709
00:38:13,550 --> 00:38:14,670
in this dark chamber?

710
00:38:15,480 --> 00:38:16,480
Why not come with me?

711
00:38:17,190 --> 00:38:19,510
I'll find another renowned physician
to treat you.

712
00:38:21,920 --> 00:38:23,550
I have no desire

713
00:38:25,230 --> 00:38:27,440
for Your Highness renowned physicians.

714
00:38:29,070 --> 00:38:30,590
Since Your Highness

715
00:38:31,000 --> 00:38:32,480
has walked in here,

716
00:38:33,030 --> 00:38:34,030
I'm afraid

717
00:38:34,880 --> 00:38:37,510
you won't be walking out
through this door again.

718
00:38:43,110 --> 00:38:45,190
The Duke must be so ill

719
00:38:46,190 --> 00:38:48,280
that you've forgotten
how to judge the situation.

720
00:38:49,550 --> 00:38:50,400
Move!

721
00:39:04,590 --> 00:39:05,360
Let us go!

722
00:39:14,480 --> 00:39:15,400
Let him go.

723
00:39:16,880 --> 00:39:17,800
Your Highness...

724
00:39:41,840 --> 00:39:43,480
I still have many questions

725
00:39:44,400 --> 00:39:45,360
to ask you.

726
00:39:48,840 --> 00:39:49,480
Your Majesty,

727
00:39:50,480 --> 00:39:51,670
the imperial golden plaque

728
00:39:51,760 --> 00:39:53,360
was not stolen by the Duke of Xie.

729
00:39:56,590 --> 00:39:57,360
Your Highness,

730
00:39:57,880 --> 00:39:59,920
wasn't that what you said yourself?

731
00:39:59,920 --> 00:40:01,070
I never said

732
00:40:01,070 --> 00:40:02,710
the Duke of Xie stole the golden plaque.

733
00:40:03,550 --> 00:40:05,070
It had been lent to Xie Yunhuai.

734
00:40:05,630 --> 00:40:06,920
Xie Yunhuai?

735
00:40:07,100 --> 00:40:09,730
He has lived on the outskirts
of the capital these past few years,

736
00:40:09,744 --> 00:40:10,800
treating the common people.

737
00:40:11,070 --> 00:40:12,400
To make traveling easier,

738
00:40:12,710 --> 00:40:14,070
I lent him

739
00:40:14,070 --> 00:40:15,190
the golden plaque.

740
00:40:15,710 --> 00:40:17,590
But he disappeared a few days ago,

741
00:40:17,744 --> 00:40:20,190
while the golden plaque
turned up in the Duke of Xie's Manor.

742
00:40:20,880 --> 00:40:22,190
That is why I concluded

743
00:40:23,550 --> 00:40:25,000
he was being held in the manor.

744
00:40:25,800 --> 00:40:26,960
Duke of Xie,

745
00:40:26,960 --> 00:40:27,920
is Yunhuai

746
00:40:28,800 --> 00:40:30,510
really in your manor?

747
00:40:31,030 --> 00:40:31,920
Your Majesty,

748
00:40:32,400 --> 00:40:34,230
Prefect Zhang has already
searched my manor.

749
00:40:34,230 --> 00:40:35,510
Did he find my son?

750
00:40:36,230 --> 00:40:37,510
Your Majesty,

751
00:40:37,510 --> 00:40:38,110
I did not.

752
00:40:38,110 --> 00:40:38,720
Your Majesty,

753
00:40:38,840 --> 00:40:40,176
Crown Prince requests an audience.

754
00:40:40,360 --> 00:40:41,030
Let him enter.

755
00:40:50,480 --> 00:40:52,480
Greetings, Father.

756
00:40:55,280 --> 00:40:57,070
Greetings, Your Majesty.

757
00:40:57,840 --> 00:40:58,960
Rise.

758
00:40:59,320 --> 00:41:01,030
What exactly happened?

759
00:41:01,110 --> 00:41:02,280
I was held in a secret chamber

760
00:41:02,280 --> 00:41:04,256
behind the wall
of the Xie family ancestral hall.

761
00:41:04,400 --> 00:41:05,710
I was fortunate to escape.

762
00:41:07,840 --> 00:41:08,480
Your Majesty,

763
00:41:09,150 --> 00:41:10,150
my son

764
00:41:10,630 --> 00:41:13,630
has long resented my remarriage.

765
00:41:14,280 --> 00:41:16,440
He has always been
prejudiced against me.

766
00:41:17,800 --> 00:41:19,150
I did not imprison him.

767
00:41:19,150 --> 00:41:19,760
I only

768
00:41:20,480 --> 00:41:23,230
wanted him to stay at the manor
so we could spend more time together

769
00:41:23,480 --> 00:41:25,630
and resolve the rift between us.

770
00:41:26,280 --> 00:41:27,280
Duke of Xie,

771
00:41:27,510 --> 00:41:29,880
you denied it outright
and concealed the truth.

772
00:41:30,440 --> 00:41:33,360
You have committed
the crime of deceiving your sovereign.

773
00:41:33,760 --> 00:41:34,920
As this is your first offense,

774
00:41:34,920 --> 00:41:36,000
your salary will
be suspended for one year.

775
00:41:36,000 --> 00:41:37,328
You are confined to your manor

776
00:41:37,400 --> 00:41:38,630
to reflect upon your conduct.

777
00:41:38,880 --> 00:41:40,440
Thank you, Your Majesty, for your mercy.

778
00:41:40,880 --> 00:41:43,960
I shall return and reflect on
my actions behind closed doors.

779
00:41:49,670 --> 00:41:51,320
Thanks, Your Majesty.

780
00:41:57,630 --> 00:41:58,230
Your Majesty,

781
00:41:58,920 --> 00:42:01,070
I have one more request.

782
00:42:01,440 --> 00:42:02,320
Speak.

783
00:42:05,880 --> 00:42:07,440
Lady Fan, the mother of Xie Yunhuai,

784
00:42:07,450 --> 00:42:09,920
was virtuous and wise,
managed the household with distinction,

785
00:42:10,280 --> 00:42:11,280
raised her children well,

786
00:42:11,280 --> 00:42:12,710
and was respected by the whole clan.

787
00:42:12,920 --> 00:42:15,280
I humbly ask Father
to issue another imperial decree,

788
00:42:15,472 --> 00:42:18,224
posthumously conferring upon Lady Fan
the title of First Rank Lady,

789
00:42:18,480 --> 00:42:20,840
so that both justice and propriety
may be upheld.

790
00:42:22,360 --> 00:42:23,230
Huayong,

791
00:42:23,320 --> 00:42:26,030
your proposal is most appropriate.

792
00:42:26,190 --> 00:42:28,510
Lady Fan's virtue

793
00:42:29,030 --> 00:42:30,480
deserves this honor.

794
00:42:31,776 --> 00:42:33,296
Why aren't you thanking His Majesty?

795
00:42:36,144 --> 00:42:37,800
Thank you
for Your Majesty's great grace.

796
00:42:38,110 --> 00:42:39,280
Thank you, Your Majesty.

797
00:42:39,280 --> 00:42:42,940
(Receiving the Mandate
and Establishing the Foundation)

798
00:42:54,590 --> 00:42:56,710
He refused to send reinforcements,

799
00:42:56,710 --> 00:42:58,150
causing Prince Qian's death,

800
00:42:58,150 --> 00:42:59,800
then claimed the throne himself!

801
00:42:59,800 --> 00:43:00,630
How dare you!

802
00:43:00,640 --> 00:43:01,880
Duke of Wei has returned.

803
00:43:01,920 --> 00:43:02,400
Youyou,

804
00:43:03,440 --> 00:43:04,280
my daughter

805
00:43:04,440 --> 00:43:06,550
isn't someone
who can be married off so easily.

806
00:43:06,550 --> 00:43:08,096
He's far too scrawny.

807
00:43:08,096 --> 00:43:10,190
How could he become
a son-in-law of the northwest?

808
00:43:10,190 --> 00:43:11,920
Only a real man like your father

809
00:43:11,920 --> 00:43:13,110
and brothers will do.

810
00:43:17,111 --> 00:43:20,051
♪I've hidden so many words♪

811
00:43:20,671 --> 00:43:23,471
♪Too reluctant to tell you♪

812
00:43:24,341 --> 00:43:31,311
♪So never uncover♪

813
00:43:31,501 --> 00:43:33,861
♪The sand that slips away
with one grasp♪

814
00:43:34,991 --> 00:43:37,721
♪The flower that withers
after one bloom♪

815
00:43:38,681 --> 00:43:44,021
♪Silently buried deep inside my heart♪

816
00:43:45,781 --> 00:43:48,601
♪Every answer I gave♪

817
00:43:49,401 --> 00:43:52,251
♪Was both bittersweet and absurd♪

818
00:43:53,041 --> 00:43:56,411
♪Hiding my tear-filled eyes
when I hurt you♪

819
00:43:56,671 --> 00:43:59,981
♪How hard it truly was?♪

820
00:44:02,951 --> 00:44:06,391
♪The wounds that healed
with just a little comfort♪

821
00:44:07,381 --> 00:44:09,711
♪The lies made whole
with a single embrace♪

822
00:44:10,981 --> 00:44:16,741
♪Pretending to be brave
as if I'd never been hurt♪

823
00:44:18,151 --> 00:44:21,281
♪It's a shame I never could♪

824
00:44:21,731 --> 00:44:24,741
♪Give you a moon in return♪

825
00:44:24,851 --> 00:44:31,491
♪With the same open heart you loved me♪

826
00:44:31,491 --> 00:44:35,161
♪I've crossed the wasteland of memories♪

827
00:44:36,031 --> 00:44:38,791
♪Never knowing I was lost♪

828
00:44:39,231 --> 00:44:42,361
♪Why don't you take me away?♪

829
00:44:42,801 --> 00:44:48,751
♪Lead me out of this endless game
of hide-and-seek♪

830
00:44:50,151 --> 00:44:53,701
♪You'll never♪

831
00:44:53,981 --> 00:45:03,451
♪Know how much I long to, long to♪

832
00:45:29,621 --> 00:45:33,101
(No animals were harmed
in the making of this film)

